OL,3,CSwansea Council calls in regulator
OL,4,Cover Cardiff Rugby takeover fears
OL,6,FSwansea Council has formally asked the
OL,7,FCompetition and Markets Authority
OL,8,F(CMA) to investigate the proposed
OL,9,Ftakeover of Cardiff Rugby, which they
OL,10,Ffear could lead to the loss of
OL,11,Fprofessional men's rugby in Swansea.
OL,13,FY11, the owners of Swansea-based
OL,14,FOspreys, are currently in discussions
OL,15,Fwith the Welsh Rugby Union (WRU) to
OL,16,Facquire Cardiff Rugby.
