OL,3,CSwansea Council calls in regulator
OL,4,Cover Cardiff Rugby takeover fears
OL,6,FThe Council's concerns focus on the
OL,7,Fproposed reduction of professional
OL,8,Fteams from four to three, the process
OL,9,Ffor allocating licences, and the
OL,10,Fpotential for one ownership group to
OL,11,Fcontrol two Welsh clubs.
OL,13,FIt believes the proposals risk
OL,14,Funfairly restricting competition,
OL,15,Freducing choice for supporters, and
OL,16,Fdamaging Swansea's economy.
OL,18,FThe Council is urging the CMA to
OL,19,Finvestigate urgently and to consider
OL,20,Finterim measures to pause the proposed
OL,21,Fdeal.
