OL,3,CSwansea Council calls in regulator
OL,4,Cover Cardiff Rugby takeover fears
OL,6,FTwo clubs in the same league being
OL,7,Fcontrolled by the same owner is
OL,8,Fbelieved to be unheard of in modern
OL,9,FEuropean sport due to concerns around
OL,10,Fsporting integrity.
OL,12,FBut it's understood that Y11 have been
OL,13,Fgiven express permission from the
OL,14,FUnited Rugby Championship to press
OL,15,Fahead with the deal.
