OL,3,CSwansea Council calls in regulator
OL,4,Cover Cardiff Rugby takeover fears
OL,6,FCllr Rob Stewart, Swansea Council
OL,7,FLeader, said: "The WRU's proposals
OL,8,Fwould mean the end of the Ospreys as a
OL,9,Fprofessional men's rugby region. This
OL,10,Fwould be a huge blow to our city -
OL,11,Feconomically, culturally and
OL,12,Femotionally.
OL,14,F"Players, supporters, residents,
OL,15,Fcommunity clubs and local businesses
OL,16,Fall deserve a fair and transparent
OL,17,Fprocess from the WRU.
