OL,3,CSwansea Council calls in regulator
OL,4,Cover Cardiff Rugby takeover fears
OL,6,F"We cannot accept a situation where
OL,7,Fdecisions are made behind closed doors
OL,8,Fto remove one of Wales's four
OL,9,Fprofessional teams and leave Swansea
OL,10,Fwithout top-level rugby.
OL,12,F"We are asking the CMA to step in
OL,13,Furgently to protect competition and
OL,14,Fgive our city and region the fair
OL,15,Ftreatment it deserves."
