OL,3,CSwansea Council calls in regulator
OL,4,Cover Cardiff Rugby takeover fears
OL,6,FThe WRU said: "We are aware that
OL,7,FSwansea Council has raised concerns
OL,8,Frelating to Welsh rugby with the UK
OL,9,FCompetition and Markets Authority
OL,10,F(CMA). As you would expect, we will
OL,11,Fconsider carefully any questions put
OL,12,Fto us by the CMA and take our own
OL,13,Fadvice. Beyond that, it would not be
OL,14,Fappropriate to comment in detail at
OL,15,Fthis stage.
