OL,3,CSwansea Council calls in regulator
OL,4,Cover Cardiff Rugby takeover fears
OL,6,F"The WRU Board has worked in good
OL,7,Ffaith over the past two years to
OL,8,Fcreate a sustainable way forward for
OL,9,FWelsh rugby in light of the
OL,10,Fsignificant financial and performance
OL,11,Fchallenges we all face.
OL,13,F"We appreciate that these are
OL,14,Fdifficult and sometimes emotive issues
OL,15,Ffor everyone involved, but our focus
OL,16,Fremains firmly on the longterm health
OL,17,Fof the whole game in Wales and on
OL,18,Fcontinuing to work constructively with
OL,19,Fall our stakeholders, including
OL,20,FSwansea Council."
