OL,6,FITV Wales has approached Ospreys for
OL,7,Fcomment.
OL,9,FOspreys CEO Lance Bradley has
OL,10,Fpreviously said: "Y11 will continue to
OL,11,Fown and operate Ospreys.
OL,13,F"If a deal for Cardiff is finalised,
OL,14,Fthis would see Y11 owning and
OL,15,Foperating both Ospreys and Cardiff,
OL,16,Fwith both regions continuing to play
OL,17,Fas separate teams.
